{"tid":701203,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫朋友問】開唔到機","createTime":"2018-06-14T03:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T08:47:35.000Z","uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fbeb888f99a7336a523a56c98bb60b5ba3e76ce4","tid":701203,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"上哂圖先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/110049_b65dd88fbb84ca866916e0899690fb0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F110049_b65dd88fbb84ca866916e0899690fb0b.jpg&h=87f21569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/110054_9ffbd26c4a4185c65a5c0c4d82ea769a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F110054_9ffbd26c4a4185c65a5c0c4d82ea769a.jpg&h=7913b30d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢部機情況係:<br />\n開機有時需要重開幾次先入到圖一既畫面，然後入到WINDOW就會出現第2張既情況<br />\n大部份時候開，螢幕都係會無畫面，但有聲可以聽到入到WINDOW<br />\n無畫面既時候有留意到所有風扇都會正常轉<br />\n<br />\nSPEC:<br />\nI5 3440<br />\n8GB DDR3 RAM<br />\n(以上兩者估計5年機齡)<br />\nRX370 4GB 顯示卡<br />\nANTEC 550W 銅牌 ( 2年)<br />\n<br />\n上次佢出事就拎左去砌機場問<br />\n話係HDD BAD DATA 但契弟我幫佢搞個陣唔覺隻舊HDD有問題<br />\n搞一輪最後都會出現上面兩張圖既問題，索性叫佢炆左隻舊HDD<br />\n換左隻新HDD之後一星期佢就咁問我究竟係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他已知情況:<br />\n清過風扇塵，散熱膏乾硬化，有提過叫佢換，不過無換到，待機溫度BIOS可見60度(多10度左右)<br />\n有畀佢另一條HDMI線試機，同樣有呢個問題<br />\n有叫佢抽插過Ｄ野，好似無甚幫助<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92057e96d8d895479176fee2b9ad1f18fd0e9315","tid":701203,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"咁冇辦法要重新砌過"},{"pid":"7692b5865872532e25a31f6eecd6cc2fe5657c0c","tid":701203,"uid":53857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"開機無畫面有聲，點解唔CHECK左張DISPLAY CARD先呢？"},{"pid":"a497a4c9b2888e1fa0933cc2c6de93f9e5cb3cea","tid":701203,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7692b5865872532e25a31f6eecd6cc2fe5657c0c","tid":701203,"uid":53857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"開機無畫面有聲，點解唔CHECK左張DISPLAY CARD先呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"有叫佢抽插過張卡<br />\n同埋都有叫佢試下用內顯開機<br />\n不過..<br />\n佢答我個茫好尻,無VGA頭 無DVI口 得HDMI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef54f6683b129853b2bdf82c983aeb26748e257","tid":701203,"uid":592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:47:35.000Z","msg":"再裝windows <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}